# Linting

After modifying any Python file, always run the linter before considering the task done:

```bash
./venv/bin/python -m ruff check pybrowser/ tests/
```

To auto-fix simple issues:
```bash
./venv/bin/python -m ruff check --fix pybrowser/ tests/
```

The project uses `ruff` configured in `pyproject.toml`. Key rules:
- No unused imports (F401)
- No undefined names (F821)
- Lines under 100 characters (E501)
- Consistent import ordering (I)
